Michael,

Your not nuts or dumb, those terms for the most part (excluding the minibox) originated on this board. The minibox is a creation of Ron Rickets, an electrical engineer out of Arlington, TX. The Shack Hack as it has become known is a modified digital radio from Radio Shack. Both of these devices work similar to Frank&#39;s box with some advantages and some disadvantages. 

The Minibox can be found at paranormalsystems.com

The instruction on how to hack the radio shack  radios, models: RS 12-469 and RS 12-470 (older version) are located at: http://www.ufogeek.com/ look under the subtitle (to the left) of Ghost Box.

Regards,

Frank R.

